<body>
    <h1>Task 14 - RAD</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"5920b6344791" id=3D"Task14-RAD-1.Introduction">1. I=
ntroduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"3ae1b67f31ca" id=3D"Task14-RAD-1.1Purpose">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"205a400e302f">The purpose of this document is to define the =
requirements for designing and implementing a multi-VPC network environment=
 across two AWS regions and establishing connectivity using <strong>Amazon =
VPC</strong> and <strong>VPC Peering</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6c0a593da7ea">The project aims to simulate a company network=
 consisting of a headquarters office and multiple branch offices hosted in =
different AWS regions.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7c781a6caf44">This document provides the design requirements=
, functional specifications, and system constraints needed to deploy and va=
lidate the network architecture.</p>
<p local-id=3D"1f941530ab00">The intended audience includes DevOps engineer=
s, cloud engineers, and infrastructure teams responsible for AWS network de=
sign.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"5eb988a43f47">
<h2 local-id=3D"3618265b8fb1" id=3D"Task14-RAD-1.2Scope">1.2 Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8ee50a9f6526">The scope of this project includes designing a=
nd implementing a multi-VPC architecture across two AWS regions.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e9a96285318b">The deployment will include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a11b5199f178">
<li local-id=3D"0e47ba52341d">
<p local-id=3D"4bcd238cb441">Creating a <strong>Headquarters VPC</strong> i=
n the region <strong>us-east-1</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"86a8d5756323">
<p local-id=3D"15166f3236a0">Creating <strong>four separate branch office V=
PCs</strong> in <strong>us-east-2</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4105a95ae147">
<p local-id=3D"b4ff6bb125e9">Designing IP addressing using <strong>Class A =
private networks for HQ</strong> and <strong>Class B private networks for b=
ranch offices</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fe038f78b464">
<p local-id=3D"0caff536b6d5">Creating required subnets for the HQ office</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"65a3ead14212">
<p local-id=3D"c61656332dae">Establishing <strong>cross-region VPC peering =
connections</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7c620eb8b380">
<p local-id=3D"abcee87a93d3">Deploying EC2 instances for connectivity testi=
ng</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a3c5068c88e6">
<p local-id=3D"d9c8e51a53d4">Updating route tables and security groups to e=
nable communication</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e9ff3d379c6b">The project focuses on <strong>learning AWS ne=
tworking architecture and connectivity concepts</strong>, rather than imple=
menting a production-grade enterprise network.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"60c837c976ba">
<h2 local-id=3D"98dd1cacc62a" id=3D"Task14-RAD-1.3Definitions,Acronyms,andA=
bbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviations</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"a=
93896a0-1a4c-4da7-98b6-264525117d02" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4b299514aa6d">
<th data-local-id=3D"5cb676acae30" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"4ff44b6d8513">Term</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"1eadaf918cff" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"a3be80e86a53">Definition</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"677ddbd0d9be">
<td data-local-id=3D"9874060a87fa" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cddb7bf83bb9">VPC</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"41f29c8e44de" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"88ec473c3565">Virtual Private Cloud =E2=80=93 isolated AWS n=
etwork environment</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4b99beb51dac">
<td data-local-id=3D"284b7ced1697" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"db56fcf2b1eb">CIDR</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"93bff14273f7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a7242592a346">Classless Inter-Domain Routing notation used f=
or IP ranges</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0397c6390358">
<td data-local-id=3D"0fad9298cdb5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3ea69d5d600e">EC2</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a2413e4428d6" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"800c1a0163e3">Elastic Compute Cloud virtual machine service<=
/p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c27051a4e3df">
<td data-local-id=3D"88d12d67c770" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6c6bc61ed5a4">Subnet</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b648ad2968ee" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4cb76ad46490">Logical subdivision of a VPC network</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2b4e180fb5ee">
<td data-local-id=3D"018d561da5fe" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ac8c35f02cae">Peering</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"141a288591d1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5d6cf69531fb">Private connection between two VPCs</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"70e58e54192d">
<td data-local-id=3D"a0da02c1031d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f9bf79b665c8">Route Table</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b007da5b05a7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ed2fb5fc7b84">Network routing configuration for subnets</p><=
/td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"29b32cdeb6ec">
<h2 local-id=3D"6b69fa0d29bd" id=3D"Task14-RAD-1.4References">1.4 Reference=
s</h2>
<p local-id=3D"428548b8d5b6">AWS VPC Documentation<br><a href=3D"https://do=
cs.aws.amazon.com/vpc" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://doc=
s.aws.amazon.com/vpc</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"2a2aa2b7f4f4">AWS VPC Peering Documentation<br><a href=3D"ht=
tps://docs.aws.amazon.com/vpc/latest/peering/" class=3D"external-link" rel=
=3D"nofollow">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/vpc/latest/peering/</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"3f27b62e9583">AWS EC2 Documentation<br><a href=3D"https://do=
cs.aws.amazon.com/ec2" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://doc=
s.aws.amazon.com/ec2</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"ff62288a626d">Networking Basics<br><a href=3D"https://aws.am=
azon.com/what-is/vpc/" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://aws=
.amazon.com/what-is/vpc/</a></p>
<hr local-id=3D"f9491dd254be">
<h2 local-id=3D"49a1653a482c" id=3D"Task14-RAD-1.5Overview">1.5 Overview</h=
2>
<p local-id=3D"7a956af49fbc">This document is organized into several sectio=
ns describing the network design and implementation requirements.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4d0eaa904752">
<li local-id=3D"5a77f48e1558">
<p local-id=3D"7879f5accae2">Section 1 introduces the purpose and scope of =
the document.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2f84bde35e96">
<p local-id=3D"71909fb4fcfa">Section 2 describes the project overview and o=
bjectives.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f8c72bcfb9fd">
<p local-id=3D"78383184fcd7">Section 3 defines functional requirements incl=
uding network design and connectivity.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5b78b9444f99">
<p local-id=3D"4a8c334a6a12">Section 4 lists non-functional requirements su=
ch as security and reliability.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a40080e00b8f">
<p local-id=3D"495041888b3a">Section 5 describes assumptions and dependenci=
es.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"58504bc901e7">
<p local-id=3D"554054b1072c">Section 6 outlines risks and mitigation strate=
gies.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4d56efe25713">
<h1 local-id=3D"1f566b35401e" id=3D"Task14-RAD-2.ProjectOverview">2. Projec=
t Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"497cf2d6f971" id=3D"Task14-RAD-2.1ProjectObjectives">2.1 Pr=
oject Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0195623500aa">The main objectives of this project are:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"26bf8ee4bd07">
<li local-id=3D"58736253ea08">
<p local-id=3D"1b837bd351dc">Design a <strong>multi-VPC network architectur=
e</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a36f9f4be75c">
<p local-id=3D"0ef2ffbf611b">Implement <strong>cross-region VPC connectivit=
y</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bfa943b5f8d">
<p local-id=3D"004a1187f96e">Allocate IP ranges using Class A and Class B a=
ddressing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae928c98b5c4">
<p local-id=3D"bb97dcbdfad6">Deploy EC2 instances for connectivity testing<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"acfdf85cc688">
<p local-id=3D"ff7cb859bc36">Validate network communication across regions<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8a837d493e30">
<h2 local-id=3D"c3987b0fab80" id=3D"Task14-RAD-2.2BusinessGoals">2.2 Busine=
ss Goals</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3a32dd300ae9">The business goals of this network design incl=
ude:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"21653e40c962">
<li local-id=3D"47ece6e9842f">
<p local-id=3D"f455ce61e2bb">Understanding multi-VPC network architecture</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1a9c573015b4">
<p local-id=3D"6ad4c447e455">Demonstrating cross-region connectivity</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"34744293c444">
<p local-id=3D"25a5aabb7d3e">Improving infrastructure segmentation using se=
parate VPCs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5c376f7bcbe">
<p local-id=3D"b33906f8a449">Simulating an inter-office cloud network</p></=
li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1eeeb103966c">
<h2 local-id=3D"663df50e0aa6" id=3D"Task14-RAD-2.3Background">2.3 Backgroun=
d</h2>
<p local-id=3D"230acf8ed250">ABC Technologies is expanding its infrastructu=
re and wants to simulate a cloud-based network architecture similar to a re=
al enterprise environment.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d7c0388b106f">The company has one headquarters office and fo=
ur branch offices located in different geographic locations.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ba7f8377d4e3">To represent this architecture in AWS, the com=
pany will deploy separate VPCs for each office and connect them using VPC P=
eering.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f2d668521003">The HQ office will host management and server =
infrastructure, while branch offices will represent remote office networks.=
</p>
<hr local-id=3D"6a226d9b5b73">
<h2 local-id=3D"fc16064c5c75" id=3D"Task14-RAD-2.4Constraints">2.4 Constrai=
nts</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d0f7a68c9e99">The following constraints apply to the project=
:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c238a106d9ba">
<li local-id=3D"35fe24a174d3">
<p local-id=3D"fb19b8a9ab40">Deployment must be completed within <strong>3 =
hours</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a27a8abbcdcd">
<p local-id=3D"5ad069ed37cb">Each office must use a <strong>separate VPC</s=
trong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"32b7dfedaf5e">
<p local-id=3D"8972018c400b">IP address ranges must not overlap</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5268c2b8f2ec">
<p local-id=3D"240dad2bfe21">HQ must use <strong>Class A private IP address=
ing</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b99deedd5c63">
<p local-id=3D"3218bdab6a73">Branch offices must use <strong>Class B privat=
e IP addressing</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2973079926f5">
<p local-id=3D"5419cf281ed6">Branch office networks must support <strong>50=
 hosts each</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"f90e263cf2e2">
<h1 local-id=3D"ba852a2b6406" id=3D"Task14-RAD-3.FunctionalRequirements">3.=
 Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"b89351edba06" id=3D"Task14-RAD-3.1UseCaseDiagram">3.1 Use C=
ase Diagram</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3201867ba384">The use case diagram illustrates how the DevOp=
s engineer interacts with AWS services to design, deploy, and verify the mu=
lti-VPC network architecture.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0932d8da1e19">The system enables network creation, cross-reg=
ion connectivity configuration, and validation of communication between VPC=
s.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper =
confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image im=
age-center" alt=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (13)-20260311-094141.png" width=
=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"b2d9d6631064384033da91afd4e121dcc8560a9830=
511cf6a12e7acfba56cfbf" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki=
/download/attachments/1846476921/Untitled%20Diagram.drawio%20(13)-20260311-=
094141.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1773222125553&amp;cacheVersio=
n=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"533" data-width=3D"1023" data-unresolved=
-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1852276752" data-linked-res=
ource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-re=
source-default-alias=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (13)-20260311-094141.png" d=
ata-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-con=
tent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1846476921" da=
ta-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-media-id=3D"4850413d-976a-4=
7ab-a214-4ba1e33c79df" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"243"></span>
<h1 local-id=3D"9872225547a5" id=3D"Task14-RAD-3.2UseCases">3.2 Use Cases</=
h1>
<hr local-id=3D"b69710058715">
<h1 local-id=3D"df03a5fa2ee8" id=3D"Task14-RAD-3.2.1UseCase1:DesignNetworkA=
rchitecture">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Design Network Architecture</h1>
<p local-id=3D"ec12ed8d2e94"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Design the multi-VPC network layout and allocate CIDR ranges.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0a8d0628f944"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"4692b7dd8fef"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"6a6bc505e3e1">
<li local-id=3D"0d8efaec0222">
<p local-id=3D"058c85c8cb47">AWS account access is available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c0844662f803">
<p local-id=3D"803533856586">Network requirements are defined</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"43af95461b73"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"0da80a1076f2">
<li local-id=3D"25ace16b69cc">
<p local-id=3D"cbc323ff9ef6">Network design with valid CIDR ranges is prepa=
red</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"371064e6e5f2"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"227c984c92b3">
<li local-id=3D"59215baa17b7">
<p local-id=3D"f52df8bec36f">Identify network regions.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"83097c5dea16">
<p local-id=3D"07dfcc0045a4">Assign Class A network range for HQ.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03eed0947e7d">
<p local-id=3D"b96f094f7e09">Assign Class B network ranges for branch offic=
es.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fdc63ada5c98">
<p local-id=3D"0ab176c36bf7">Ensure CIDR blocks do not overlap.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"f880a62574fa"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"8094ae20846a">
<li local-id=3D"bc40bbe73ecf">
<p local-id=3D"d42b08aeed2d">IP overlap detected =E2=86=92 redesign CIDR al=
location.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"562093c7ae2c">
<h1 local-id=3D"4e3b46508381" id=3D"Task14-RAD-3.2.2UseCase2:CreateAWSVPCEn=
vironment">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Create AWS VPC Environment</h1>
<p local-id=3D"e38c52a5ac9f"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Create required VPCs and subnets in AWS.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5f33cac41eda"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"973384236a9e"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f2371dc6fc5a">
<li local-id=3D"d5b255b04e41">
<p local-id=3D"4ecbdd015486">Network design is finalized</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"32b3a9e94d0d"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a645fc442b42">
<li local-id=3D"5dace091e69b">
<p local-id=3D"12220af887f3">HQ and branch VPCs are created successfully</p=
></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b45a7d77c11b"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"5dd0444f6d8d">
<li local-id=3D"59e5f00fd987">
<p local-id=3D"e716b34f0b6e">Create HQ VPC in us-east-1.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9da7b5354d7">
<p local-id=3D"e89204e62975">Create server subnet.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"189b2f72e5d2">
<p local-id=3D"e3b90b81ddcd">Create management subnet.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5e9715ed8107">
<p local-id=3D"7d980c6646c2">Create four branch VPCs in us-east-2.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a8c6fc7e64ca">
<p local-id=3D"3af4a29485c9">Configure subnets for each branch office.</p><=
/li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"8a502537c417"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"0452fe402825">
<li local-id=3D"9302f7f3638a">
<p local-id=3D"991233c6b1f3">Incorrect CIDR configuration =E2=86=92 update =
VPC settings.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d3217b55c2e1">
<h1 local-id=3D"b49279b6d2f6" id=3D"Task14-RAD-3.2.3UseCase3:ConfigureVPCPe=
ering">3.2.3 Use Case 3: Configure VPC Peering</h1>
<p local-id=3D"c1014b17d0d1"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Create VPC peering connections between HQ and each branch office.</p>
<p local-id=3D"35cdb569c622"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"191bcf7b00eb"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"eb08ca06b1f4">
<li local-id=3D"9a9f7479f22f">
<p local-id=3D"1b24d53d4996">VPCs exist in AWS</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4950788239a2"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3c2692056900">
<li local-id=3D"e76a2a6dfdf6">
<p local-id=3D"916941e06fec">Cross-region connectivity between HQ and branc=
h offices is established</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f8d6d573d395"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"70d392bba166">
<li local-id=3D"cfac7968cb35">
<p local-id=3D"605df65adb33">Create VPC peering request.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e31ca102e06a">
<p local-id=3D"20bb2d69a78f">Accept peering connection.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"191f77fd128a">
<p local-id=3D"51036f9f1711">Update route tables.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bdea12ed24f9">
<p local-id=3D"d89692176789">Verify routing configuration.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"f3b083fcf5e0"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"baeab12a47df">
<li local-id=3D"74899be2bda6">
<p local-id=3D"504214bd9a6f">Routing misconfiguration =E2=86=92 update rout=
e tables.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3a498908bf68">
<h1 local-id=3D"f3daf1b7b9bc" id=3D"Task14-RAD-3.2.4UseCase4:DeployEC2Insta=
ncesandTestConnectivity">3.2.4 Use Case 4: Deploy EC2 Instances and Test Co=
nnectivity</h1>
<p local-id=3D"76a6ac62ca7a"><strong>Description</strong><br>
Deploy EC2 instances in each VPC and verify connectivity.</p>
<p local-id=3D"40617481f46a"><strong>Actors</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"8d3882bffd48"><strong>Preconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"e554e34fa931">
<li local-id=3D"22c01a867941">
<p local-id=3D"cc83b044c8d2">VPC peering connections are active</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1b5e4a0983fc"><strong>Postconditions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9e6ed2987a5a">
<li local-id=3D"6d777361cb6d">
<p local-id=3D"6abc1ccf542e">Successful communication between HQ and branch=
 offices</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"600bb99cd430"><strong>Flow of Events</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"af67e7ac0712">
<li local-id=3D"46f59674abff">
<p local-id=3D"424f71351a08">Launch EC2 instances in HQ subnets.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e730bd6bef57">
<p local-id=3D"0567436fbb2c">Launch EC2 instances in branch VPCs.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b76342929ba3">
<p local-id=3D"b5814e8c19dd">Configure security groups.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff0586ac6cee">
<p local-id=3D"d768e8e867e2">Perform connectivity testing using network com=
mands.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"603af17281b0"><strong>Alternative Flows</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"59428dd51612">
<li local-id=3D"b40b6962ec94">
<p local-id=3D"cb17e228eab6">Connection failure =E2=86=92 check route table=
s and security groups.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"58d0fa1b5336">
<h1 local-id=3D"33a81e3f03a3" id=3D"Task14-RAD-4.Non-FunctionalRequirements=
">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"6c02b8d7c1ed" id=3D"Task14-RAD-4.1PerformanceRequirements">=
4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"0471dc537311">
<li local-id=3D"142e33d84d58">
<p local-id=3D"9a559d280b6a">Network latency should remain within acceptabl=
e limits for cross-region connectivity.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b420c27f657d">
<p local-id=3D"dae54a6084e2">Route table updates must propagate immediately=
 after configuration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"cf2398654842">
<h2 local-id=3D"c05ef4e7a6c7" id=3D"Task14-RAD-4.2SecurityRequirements">4.2=
 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"70d0dcc32414">
<li local-id=3D"6d1881e65039">
<p local-id=3D"b65281970e2a">Security groups must allow only required testi=
ng ports.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"55c64be0d7e0">
<p local-id=3D"654787ecd835">Network access must remain restricted to inter=
nal VPC communication.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b8a86d5172ce">
<h2 local-id=3D"e5e1d43210a3" id=3D"Task14-RAD-4.3UsabilityRequirements">4.=
3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"769e17abeda2">
<li local-id=3D"6a08bad8a544">
<p local-id=3D"e7b8fc96dbf9">The network design should be easy to understan=
d and document.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"735fc9efc289">
<p local-id=3D"8e5e372dece5">Naming conventions should clearly represent HQ=
 and branch offices.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e9b0b49f6301">
<h2 local-id=3D"96d26ad8695d" id=3D"Task14-RAD-4.4ReliabilityRequirements">=
4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"a1a439d262a5">
<li local-id=3D"a510314f8ff3">
<p local-id=3D"a8022f7d4e93">VPC peering connections must remain stable dur=
ing testing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d8d5768ff372">
<p local-id=3D"0bfa3a3a3f1f">EC2 instances must remain reachable for networ=
k testing.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"f0fc3d67cff0">
<h2 local-id=3D"82aa00d02fe9" id=3D"Task14-RAD-4.5ComplianceRequirements">4=
.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"914a230bb0d1">
<li local-id=3D"a94a3911b202">
<p local-id=3D"59eb8120106a">Follow AWS networking best practices.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4fd090a527cd">
<p local-id=3D"284cf379bb37">Ensure IP addressing complies with private net=
work standards.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7cf637709376">
<h1 local-id=3D"7b2d422ea079" id=3D"Task14-RAD-5.AssumptionsandDependencies=
">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"83ad08d4171b" id=3D"Task14-RAD-5.1Assumptions">5.1 Assumpti=
ons</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"24fd445f5698">
<li local-id=3D"de4e950ac790">
<p local-id=3D"a4a10c355ba4">AWS account permissions allow VPC creation.</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"2ddfb814d680">
<p local-id=3D"261aa8c03fe9">Required AWS regions are accessible.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1d4f80416348">
<p local-id=3D"a06bfbb3a509">Security groups are correctly configured.</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ed98f543fad8">
<h2 local-id=3D"27504e23877f" id=3D"Task14-RAD-5.2Dependencies">5.2 Depende=
ncies</h2>
<p local-id=3D"721f3b98e915">The project depends on:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8ede7add11b1">
<li local-id=3D"73b58bb6375f">
<p local-id=3D"5b445b87e0b8">AWS VPC services</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9f659e044abf">
<p local-id=3D"058ea12cd734">AWS EC2 instances</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"38057872ba9c">
<p local-id=3D"abd802a00e45">Internet connectivity for management access</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"9a456ff5e086">
<p local-id=3D"af1c143cf647">VPC Peering support between regions</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"374c018583e1">
<h1 local-id=3D"968eb0544ece" id=3D"Task14-RAD-6.RiskAnalysis">6. Risk Anal=
ysis</h1>
